{"tid":2004260,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩會2020】彭博：中國據悉考慮不設今年GDP增長數字","createTime":"2020-05-06T10:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T01:09:52.000Z","uid":343294,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf286cfdf50920682e81283466c5e3b99fa0b4e","tid":2004260,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"【兩會2020】彭博：中國據悉考慮不設今年GDP增長數字<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;國情動向&nbsp;18:05&nbsp;2020/05/06&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社報道，中國據悉考慮不設2020年國內生產總值(GDP)增長數字。<br />\n內地本月底召開全國兩會，按過去慣例，年度GDP目標會在政府工作報告中列出。<br />\n央行貨幣政策委員馬駿此前表示，受新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情影響，今年GDP增速很難實現6%的目標，實現4%至5%增速的難度也很大，建議中國今年不再設定GDP增長目標，否則可能會綁架宏觀政策，最後被迫搞「大水漫灌」。<br />\n<br />\n中國首季度GDP按年下跌6.8%，為1992年中國開始公佈季度GDP數據以來首次出現負值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2636058?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2636058%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=cf68eb7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2636058?r=cpstni</a>"},{"pid":"3589995bd63809fc3aa641e76a61c05104ccbb5a","tid":2004260,"uid":73092,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"無標準就唔會低過標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50c22d0eba74394e5535cfad97c212ba5c8ce66","tid":2004260,"uid":321977,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"是但啦，下年仲有無中國都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e608e522f183f773c29b0d3dee428d1cfde58cdc","tid":2004260,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"報喜不報憂 一貫做法"},{"pid":"db24eb0c43e0d5422d9168583b304c922f43b6a9","tid":2004260,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"仲增長？ 倒退都嚟唔切喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346782d97c8cf751b6f86c7